{{Infobox dungeon |name = Pokéball Factory |image = [[File:Pokéball Factory.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Pokéball Factory. |tokens = 615,000 |location = North of Laverre City }} '''Pokéball Factory''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 8,173,950 HP.
